rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0001
rows.name:
There's supposed to be a totally
amazing view through here!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0002
rows.name: I'm so pumped for this!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0003
rows.name:
That interests you? I cannot say the
same.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0004
rows.name:
Aw, come on, lighten up! We can go
together. It'll be fun!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0005
rows.name:
You could bring an army and it would
still not interest me.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0006
rows.name: I'm going on ahead.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0007
rows.name:
Hey, hold up Seori! Don't go out
on your own!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0008
rows.name:
Seori, why are you being so cold
to me?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0009
rows.name:
It's nothing personal. I'm equally cold
to everyone.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0010
rows.name: Even to my Driver, it is the same.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0011
rows.name: Yeah, I guess that's true.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0012
rows.name:
That's right. Seori's a cool kind
of gal.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0013
rows.name:
I can't deny that. Though I don't think
it's a bad thing per se.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0014
rows.name:
True, that. But that's just her
character.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0015
rows.name:
Uhh... That's not what I mean. What
I'm trying to say is...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0016
rows.name: I promised you. The old you.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0017
rows.name: I promised that I wouldn't forget you.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0018
rows.name:
The old you wanted the two of us to
stay friends.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0019
rows.name: Which is why...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0020
rows.name:
I don't see why you would go to such
lengths.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0021
rows.name:
The present me doesn't think the same
way.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0022
rows.name:
And both you and I have lost our
memories once before.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0023
rows.name: Ah...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0024
rows.name: How should I respond?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0025
rows.name: Try to consider Mikumari's feelings.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0026
rows.name: You know, you two are really alike.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0027
rows.name: How should I respond?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0028
rows.name: Try to consider Mikumari's feelings.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0029
rows.name: Y'know, you two are really alike.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0030
rows.name: How should I respond?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0031
rows.name: Try to consider Mikumari's feelings.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0032
rows.name: You two are really quite alike.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0033
rows.name: How should I respond?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0034
rows.name: Maybe consider Mikumari's feelings?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0035
rows.name: You two are pretty similar really.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0101
rows.name: Sorry.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0102
rows.name: I'm not trying to be cold to her.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0103
rows.name: It's OK. I understand.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0104
rows.name:
I'm just another Blade to you. Nothing
more, nothing less. I get it.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0105
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0106
rows.name: But it's different for me.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0107
rows.name:
I knew the old you. I wanted to be
together with you, always.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0201
rows.name: We are alike?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0202
rows.name:
The old Mikumari was never really
bothered about her memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0203
rows.name:
And that seemed to make the
previous Seori really sad.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0204
rows.name:
The old Mikumari was never really
bothered about her memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0205
rows.name:
And it looked like that made the
previous Seori really sad.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0206
rows.name:
The old Mikumari didn't care very
much about her memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0207
rows.name:
And I got the impression that fact
made the previous Seori quite sad.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0208
rows.name:
The old Mikumari hardly cared about
her memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0209
rows.name:
And that seemed to upset the
old Seori one heck of a lot.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0210
rows.name:
And that's why you're sad? Because
you knew the former me?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0211
rows.name:
I'm not that sad about it. Yet. But if this
keeps up, I might just start crying.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0212
rows.name: Haha...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0214
rows.name: You two are like sisters!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0215
rows.name:
Though I guess it's weird for Blades
to have sisters...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0216
rows.name: You two are basically sisters.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0217
rows.name:
Though I guess it's kinda funny for
Blades to have sisters, huh...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0218
rows.name: You two are essentially sisters.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0219
rows.name:
Though perhaps sisters is the wrong
word, considering you're both Blades...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0220
rows.name: You're basically sisters, right?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0221
rows.name:
Though it isn't half strange for Blades
to have sisters...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0222
rows.name: Sisters...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0223
rows.name: I like that!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0224
rows.name: You're happy with this?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0225
rows.name: Heck yeah! It makes us sound special!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0226
rows.name:
I can be the older sister, and you can
be the younger one!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0227
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0228
rows.name:
Seori, would you mind calling me
"Onee-chan"?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0229
rows.name: No way!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0230
rows.name: I guess you've gotta warm to it, huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0231
rows.name:
Well, my dear younger sister, you can call me 
"Onee-chan" any time you want!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0232
rows.name: I will never call you that.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0233
rows.name: Looks like we've got a long way ahead[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0234
rows.name: Still, thank you!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0235
rows.name:
I was worried for a while, but I think
I'll be able to keep our promise now!
